      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, providing a direct connection to the M Variable Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. The suspension maintains excellent damping characteristics with refreshed bushings, preserving the chassis's neutral handling and high-speed stability. While the exterior and interior exhibit minor patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain is dialed-in, offering a linear 8,000 RPM redline experience and precise heel-and-toe downshifts.",
